    <h4 align="center">Cummings Park</h4>
<p align="center">All four postcards are undated. They appear to be of the 1930s and 1940s from the look of the bathing costumes. </p>
    <table width="100%" align="center"  cellpadding="2" summary="this table contains images, a caption and related text.">
      
      <tr align="center" valign="bottom">
        <td width="50%"><img src="images/shippanpc04_11w.jpg" alt="Undated postcard titled 'The Pavilion, Cummings Park, Stamford, Conn.'" width="471" height="305"></td>
        <td width="50%"><img src="images/shippanpc04_14w.jpg" alt="Undated postcard titled 'Bathing Pavilion and Beach, Cummings Park, Stamford, Conn.'" width="471" height="305"></td>
      </tr>
      <tr align="center" valign="bottom">
        <td><img src="images/shippanpc04_17w.jpg" alt="Undated postcard titled 'Beach and Pavilion, Cummings Park, Stamford, Conn.'" title="Beach and Pavilion, Cummings Park" width="469" height="305"></td><td><img src="images/shippanpc04_16w.jpg" alt="Undated postcard titled 'Along the Beach, Stamford, Conn., Beauty on the Beach.'" title="'Along the Beach, Stamford, Conn., Beauty on the Beach'" width="480" height="301"></td>
      </tr>
